snippet.title: Legend - Super Nintendo Gameplay (Steam Re-Release)
snippet.description:
Arcade Zone's 1994 SNES beat'em up is digitally re-released on Steam, so it might be worth taking a look.

Legend (1994) (C) Piko Interactive
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/412380/Legend_1994/
